Package edu.cmu.commons.data.io

Interface Summary
Deserializer<E> Capable of populating an entity with data parsed from an InputStream.
Serialization<E> Couples Serializer and Deserializer interfaces.
Serializer<E> Capable of writing data from an entity to an OutputStream.
